verbose_text: In agreement with previous data, non atherosclerotic Siglec-G -/- mice have--compared to Siglec-G +/+ control mice--significantly increased numbers of B-1a cells in the spleen, increased numbers of CD138 + plasmablasts (B220 +) and plasma cells (B220 lo) in the spleen and bone marrow, and increased levels of OSE specific IgM antibodies in the plasma (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A-S1G).
